<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I can't believe how long it took me to sell this item (on E'ci)!  For rogues with high Dex, this is like a mini-Ykesha!  It's got a fast delay, OK damage, it procs a decent DD spell, AND it lowers target AC!  And it took me 3 days of standing around auctioning to sell it for the 450pp I got for it?!?!?  What a world...<BR>
<BR>
The weird part is, it was a gnome mage who ended up buying it.  All you rogues on E'ci - what were you thinking? ;-)  If my paladin could have used piercing, I'd have dropped my lousy tomahawk for this weapon in a second!</font></td></tr></table>
