<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Pyrja</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-05-20 04:21:44</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>    THIS is the MOST amazing weapon for a low lvl enchanter twink, let me explain to you why.  First, as was stated this drops off of a mid 20s mob, I camped him AND the foreman one night for several hours and we got lucky and EACH of us got a shard (I got a scimmy off of the foreman too heheh).  Anyways I give this to my enchanter and nothing, I keep using my mithril quill to get the HP boost, and try this from time to time. Finally I hit 16th lvl, and 3 strikes later kerpow! the effect goes off, went 2 times in the first battle and turned a tough fight into an easy one. Now what what make this especially attractive to ENCHANTERS is the fact that all of the charisma enhancing items made with star-rubies in jewelling skill, provide DEXTERITY bonuses as well. I am an enchanter with 110 dex and this thing goes off constantly. <BR>
<BR>
     As a side note I am putting together a rogue, and somewhere around 25th lvl as an enchanter when I go to 2 steins with no weapon, my rogue may be nearing 16th and will find this weapon VERY handy.</font></td></tr></table>
